metadata.name: ANXTY [SE]
metadata.description:
Will our hearts ever stop feeling ANXTY?  Stop worrying so much, expecting so much?  

Will our hearts ever stop being wrapped in barbed wire? Hit hard and fast without getting hurt?  

Will we ever really be free of ourselves? Of our own toughts?


/// BETTER EXPERIENCED WITH HEADPHONES
